    "created_at": "2022-10-11T22:41:38Z",
    "updated_at": "2022-10-12T01:39:11Z",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I solved this problem with a little \"hack\", it's not the best solution, but solve the problem in a CI pipeline or for new installations. \r\nBasically, I added these scripts in package.json:\r\n\r\n```\r\n \"scripts\": {    \r\n    \"preinstall\": \"mkdir tasksCopy && cp -r tasks/* tasksCopy && rm -rf tasks && mkdir tasks && touch tasks/index.ts\",\r\n    \"postinstall\": \"cp -r tasksCopy/* tasks && rm -rf tasksCopy\",\r\n    \"install\": \"preinstall && yarn install && postinstall\"\r\n    }\r\n```",
